The "Why" (Very Important for Interviews)

Interviewers often ask "Why do we need this?"


Pod            → To run containers.

ReplicaSet     → Because Pods can die.

Deployment     → Because ReplicaSets can't do rolling updates.

StatefulSet    → Because databases need stable names and storage.

DaemonSet      → Because every node needs logging/monitoring agents.

Job            → Because some tasks should run only once.

CronJob        → Because some tasks must run on a schedule.

Service        → Because Pod IPs change.

Ingress        → Because we don't want one LoadBalancer per Service.

ConfigMap      → Because configuration should be separate from code.

Secret         → Because passwords shouldn't be stored in images or ConfigMaps.

PV/PVC         → Because Pods are ephemeral but data must persist.

StorageClass   → Because storage should be created automatically.

HPA            → Because traffic changes over time.

RBAC           → Because not everyone should have cluster-admin access.
